data.title: Alexander Gordon
data.meta_description:
Alexander Gordon, born on 20 February, 1964, Russia, is a Russian TV-show host, radio host, journalist, actor and director. 
	He has won Taffy award in 2008, and is known as Russia's best TV-host, for his show "Private Showing"
